nodes.text: A female Cerean was a member of the Rebel Alliance who was imprisoned by Imperials on the planet Radhii. She and other four members escaped and hide in the Zoess, a large forest near the city Tavuu. The Imperials hired Gorlan Seba to help them find them. Later they found each other, but their fight was halted by a hologram recording of Leia Organa, who spread the message of the destruction of the second Death Star and the death of the Emperor.
